{"tid":1276191,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"發夢夢見催淚彈嘅正確應對方法","createTime":"2019-07-02T01:55:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-02T02:00:30.000Z","uid":91659,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2962ef18510800fb52b947f7637a99d6ab2c93a4","tid":1276191,"uid":91659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T01:55:08.000Z","msg":"之前發夢夢見意大利友人嘅經驗分享，佢地一班人經常面對意大利示威遊行，催淚彈食唔少。而佢地係會隨手帶備一個切開嘅<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">檸檬</span></span><br />\n<br />\n冇錯，就係檸檬。雖然研究冇證實檸檬汁能夠預防催淚彈，但係大量歐洲示威者都會用檸檬黎減低催淚彈對眼睛嘅不適同中和 chemical 以免刺激肺部。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n通常用法係，事前先將檸檬切成 wedges, 面對催淚氣體時先將檸檬汁捈喺眼皮同眼底，然後咬住舊檸檬黎中和即將吸入嘅空氣。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢招聽落都幾土法煉鋼，不過咁多人用，應該有一定嘅減輕效果。<br />\n<br />\n有冇巴絲親身試過 report 下功效？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔知青檸得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過青檸好貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以下附上檸檬正確使用介紹<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/SX_ViT4Ra7k\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FSX_ViT4Ra7k&d=nd52c%2FRhS%2BUv0SpwCnLJ%2BvilxGv0e2UEk%2F7kpEYl8nk%3D&h=9fe2eaaf\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/SX_ViT4Ra7k</a><br />\n<br />\n香港加油，一齊走落去！"},{"pid":"087294d076042a719c50dde83c275a60983686e5","tid":1276191,"uid":116734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T01:57:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c082b2f767f627ce296ddb192f4435be6b9e4de","tid":1276191,"uid":16061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T01:59:32.000Z","msg":"檸檬汁入眼會點？"},{"pid":"23d590e021b2117d14a57e24b368e671938c6ab5","tid":1276191,"uid":94819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T02:00:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}